  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2 \u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We presented Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa said that Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma also submitted for the election of a President from the Parliament and that the goal face struggle should end now. He said this while speaking to the media after the parliamentary session.",
        "\"We are waiting to see how it will turn out. No matter what government comes, we will serve the people of the country. (Regarding the replacement of the government) the party has not yet taken a decision.",
        "I work according to the decisions taken by our party. We presented Dallas. We voted. So lost. Someone wins. Winners win. Losers lost. (Golfface Struggle) Now it's enough.\""
      ],
